s2a-api
=======

Ship2Anywhere API client library

Services
========
Service modules are located at s2a_api/

1. Quote Service
   The 'Get quote' service allows for obtaining shipping quotes from carriers integrated with Ship2Anywhere.
   
   Constructor arguments:
        - api_url: root URL for API service, eg. https://api.s2asandbox.com/v1.0/quote/
    
   Method: get_quote:
        - arguments: dictionary compilant with JSON structure for Quote Request
        - return value: dictionary compilant with JSON structure for Quote Response
    
    # import s2a_api client
    from s2a_api import logutil
    from s2a_api import quote
    from s2a_api.exception import S2aApiException
    
    # create object
    api_url = "https://api.s2asandbox.com/v1.0/"
    quote_service = quote.QuoteService(api_url)
    
    # get quote
    json_data = {} # ... add JSON structure for Quote Service 
    r = quote_service.get_quote(json_data) # method returns dictionary
                                           # compilant with JSON structure
                                           # for Quote Response
    
